{"tid":218714,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"男友係邊個都冇所謂 因為我只有想到我自己？","createTime":"2017-04-26T16:30:27.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-27T00:51:53.000Z","uid":61560,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"e4423aa37febd8f2d3d8ecd02af9aeaa010fd092","tid":218714,"uid":61560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T16:30:27.000Z","msg":"同男朋友一齊左兩年，都仲係好sweet<br />\n佢成日都話我好掛住你呀，<br />\n好希望呢刻我喺佢身邊etc<br />\n咁我都梗係會話我都係啦。<br />\n<br />\n我每次拍拖都好投入，但散左後好快會復原，<br />\n然後搵第二個。<br />\n我對男朋友好好，好錫佢，絕對唔會帽佢。<br />\n但近呢幾年，我發覺無論對象係邊個，<br />\n我對佢嘅態度都會係一樣。<br />\n與其話我掛住我男朋友，<br />\n不如話我想有人陪，對方係邊個其實都冇所謂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n每次講「我愛你」我都會質疑自己係咪真係愛佢定愛男朋友呢個存在。<br />\n<br />\n咁樣係咪好唔正常？定其實好多人都咁諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1012ad82805074c2bad262a9d680752e171c444b","tid":218714,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T16:34:15.000Z","msg":"如果深愛 就無辦法失去 無人可以代替<br />\n呢個世界邊有咁多真愛 只有好感同磨合"},{"pid":"dd9f1aa8ada744e5207c115291e35c4df2301cf9","tid":218714,"uid":61560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T16:50:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>如果深愛 就無辦法失去 無人可以代替<br />\n呢個世界邊有咁多真愛 只有好感同磨合</blockquote><br />\n從未有呢個「呢個人無法失去嘅感覺」<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0568822b41ac37fc6e9543444aa7dad1b4af300","tid":218714,"uid":111175,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T16:51:15.000Z","msg":"I know that feel sis<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb23c68fb5f2caaf9f73e5c71948d6adca6c59b6","tid":218714,"uid":79974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T16:52:07.000Z","msg":"臭西！"},{"pid":"a2b15be525293ccfec7eab67e55d5bbe4beb1c8a","tid":218714,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T16:53:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>如果深愛 就無辦法失去 無人可以代替<br />\n呢個世界邊有咁多真愛 只有好感同磨合</blockquote><br />\n從未有呢個「呢個人無法失去嘅感覺」<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n喊都唔會喊？"},{"pid":"4c1e300cc7c4823dbb6c6ebbd85554e0b0dc527a","tid":218714,"uid":89572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T16:56:48.000Z","msg":"有啲明白&hellip;<br />\n分手果陣傷心左半個月<br />\n之後有人溝&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就好快唔再傷心<br />\n我都唔想架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4601e70891ffd323526bef7a369ee34d239f3bc3","tid":218714,"uid":55249,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T17:03:40.000Z","msg":"你應該係人地對你好 你就會對返人地好 因為我都有呢種諗法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8f14493cc92e1463f0c57169b1e3bc42ab761e4","tid":218714,"uid":78295,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T17:18:27.000Z","msg":"只要溝通到價值觀近就無所謂"},{"pid":"0a0f8b6662c25c582c2f604761028e883e7092cc","tid":218714,"uid":61560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T18:05:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>如果深愛 就無辦法失去 無人可以代替<br />\n呢個世界邊有咁多真愛 只有好感同磨合</blockquote><br />\n從未有呢個「呢個人無法失去嘅感覺」<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n喊都唔會喊？</blockquote><br />\n有 但一個星期就冇晒事<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7bb42b212fbce52603df9f4c43bceab1f469959","tid":218714,"uid":61560,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-26T18:06:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有啲明白&hellip;<br />\n分手果陣傷心左半個月<br />\n之後有人溝&hellip;<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就好快唔再傷心<br />\n我都唔想架<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/17.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nexact7ly<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我係咪臭西"},{"pid":"eff11ce4fbb44eb9a3f82ab427ea5a561b947c71","tid":218714,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit